README --

Having created YOURSERVER, a fresh Ubuntu Lucid machine on Rackspace, you can
deploy CouchDB over HTTPS by entering the following commands in a shell on your
local UNIX or UNIX-based workstation:

    $ curl http://quanah.googlecode.com/hg/server/Makefile .
    $ scp Makefile root@YOURSERVER
    $ ssh root@YOURSERVER make

                                                            -- SRW, 28 May 2010
